# This syncs Clerk user IDs to Supabase RLS policies

# ==================================================
# MONGODB ("THOUGHTS" - Agent Traces)
# ==================================================
# Get from MongoDB Atlas: https://cloud.mongodb.com
# Create a free M0 cluster, then get connection string from:
# Clusters → Connect → Connect your application → Node.js driver
